&lt;h1&gt;General Porter - Band 2&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited to join Royal United Hospital Bath NHS Foundation Trust Portering Services. The portering service provides a range of services, including patient movement, transportation of equipment; tasks will include driving Trust vehicles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A clean, valid driving license is essential criteria for all applicants.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for reliable, motivated, and flexible individuals with good communication and interpersonal skills suited to the special needs of a hospital environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants should be able to undertake shift and weekend working at either of our hospital site and be able to meet the physical demands of the post&lt;/p&gt;
